docs.lead_paragraph: The canvass for Speaker or the House of Representatives has already commenced at Washington. The Washington Star states that the President and his Cabinet will take no part in the contest, nor seek to influence its decision in any way.

headline.main: THE OTTOMAN PORTE.; Course of Turkish Reform.

docs.lead_paragraph: Turkish return began with SALIM III. In 1789--an eventful European year. This Sultan especially endeavored to change the system of the Turkish armies, which the adverse formers of his war with Russia had prosed to be so interior to their enemies.

docs.lead_paragraph: THE ACT FOR THE PREVENTION OF CONTAGIOUS AND EPIDEMIC DISEASES.--The act of Parliament under which the order in Council respecting the cholera was issued, passed on the 4th of September, 1848. It is entitled "An Act to Renew and Amend an Act of the 10th year of Her present Majesty, for the more speedy removal of certain nuisances and the prevention of contagious and epidemic diseases."

headline.main: NEW-YORK CITY.; TWO MURDER CASES. The South-street Stabbing Affair-Homicide in the Second Ward.

docs.lead_paragraph: Yesterday morning, Coroner GAMBLE held an investigation at the New York Hospital, concerning the recent stabbing affair in South-street, near Dover, which resulted in the death of a young man named DENNIS COLLINS, who was wounded in the ab omen by a dirk in the hands of a sailor, named THOMAS MURPHY.

docs.lead_paragraph: A railroad leading out of a city, making the Very largest allowance for accidents, undoubtedly saves, in the course of a year, ten, or we might rather say, a hundred times as many lives as it destroys. The number of persons killed, fearful as the aggregate is, forms a small proportion to the number whose lives are saved by thee opportunities afforded of leaving the City during the Summer months.
